On what operating system --&amp;gt; Win7/64 bit
What browser are you using --&amp;gt; Chrome 16.0.912.36 (Official Build 109393)
&lt;b&gt;Please include version information for both the OS and the browser.&lt;/b&gt;

&lt;b&gt;What steps will reproduce the problem?&lt;/b&gt;
1. Go through the steps in Nacl SDK Test plan
2. Start the local host server in Step 5
3. Quit the server by using localhost:5103?quit=1 from the browser
4. Info is shown that Server is shutting down on 5103
5. Relaunch chrome and make sure that local host has been shut down.

&lt;b&gt;What is the expected output?&lt;/b&gt;
Local host should be shut down in a while.

&lt;b&gt;What do you see instead?&lt;/b&gt;
waited almost for 15-20 mins, to proceed to step 6 in which there is an another step to start the local host server. The server which was ran in Step 5 is not yet shut down.




